event DebugVerify(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s, address signer)
event MetaTransactionExecuted(address indexed from, address indexed verifier, bool indexed verified)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
function _verify(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s) view returns (bool)
function eip712Domain() view returns (bytes1 fields, string name, string version, uint256 chainId, address verifyingContract, bytes32 salt, uint256[] extensions)
function execute(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, bytes proof, bytes32[] publicInputs, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s) payable returns (bool)
function executeWithSignature(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, bytes proof, bytes32[] publicInputs, bytes signature) payable returns (bool)
